es to display on the author\'s profile page:'=>'Iru ifiweranṣẹ lati ṣe afihan lori oju-iwe profaili onkọwe:','Posts'=>'Ifiweranṣẹ','Posts by %1$s'=>'Ifiweranṣẹ nipasẹ %1$s','Posts by %s'=>'Ifiweranṣẹ nipasẹ %s','Prev'=>'Tẹsiwaju','Preview'=>'Ṣayẹwo','Pro feature'=>'Ẹya Pro','Published date'=>'Ọjọ ti a tẹjade','Published posts of the following post types: %s'=>'Ifiweranṣẹ ti a tẹjade ti iru ifiweranṣẹ wọnyi: %s','PublishPress'=>'PublishPress','PublishPress Authors'=>'PublishPress Awọn Onkọwe','PublishPress Authors allows you to add multiple authors and guest authors to WordPress posts'=>'PublishPress Awọn Onkọwe gba ọ laaye lati fi ọpọlọpọ awọn onkọwe ati awọn onkọwe alejo kun si awọn ifiweranṣẹ WordPress','PublishPress Authors Box'=>'Aago Awọn Onkọwe PublishPress','PublishPress Authors needs a database update for Permissions integration.'=>'PublishPress Awọn Onkọwe nilo imudojuiwọn ibi ipamọ fun isopọmọ Awọn igbanilaaye.','PublishPress Authors Pro allows you to unlock the full potential of Author Categories.'=>'PublishPress Awọn Onkọwe Pro gba ọ laaye lati ṣii agbara kikun ti Awọn Ẹka Onkọwe.','PublishPress Authors Settings'=>'Awọn Eto PublishPress Awọn Onkọwe','PublishPress Blocks has over 20 extra Gutenberg blocks including accordions, galleries, tables, and more.'=>'PublishPress Blocks ni ju 20 awọn bulọọki Gutenberg afikun pẹlu awọn accordion, awọn ile-iṣere, awọn tabili, ati diẹ sii.','PublishPress Blocks is a free plugin with full support for PublishPress Authors.'=>'PublishPress Blocks jẹ afikun ọfẹ pẹlu atilẹyin kikun fun PublishPress Awọn Onkọwe.','Quick Edit'=>'Ṣatunkọ Yara','Quick edit &#8220;%s&#8221; inline'=>'Ṣatunkọ yara &#8220;%s&#8221; inlin','Quick&nbsp;Edit'=>'Yara&nbsp;Ṣatunkọ','Random'=>'Aiyedun','Rank Math Seo Integration'=>'Isopọ Rank Math Seo','Read more.'=>'Ka siwaju.','Recent Post Title Border Bottom Style'=>'Iru Akojọ Ifiweranṣẹ Tuntun Iwọn Ààrin','Recent Post Title Border Color'=>'Icolor Ààrin Iru Akojọ Ifiweranṣẹ Tuntun','Recent Post Title Border Width'=>'Iwọn Ààrin Iru Akojọ Ifiweranṣẹ Tuntun','Recent Post Title Color'=>'Icolor Iru Akojọ Ifiweranṣẹ Tuntun','Recent Post Types'=>'Iru Akojọ Ifiweranṣẹ Tuntun','Recent Posts Alignment'=>'Iṣọkan Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ Tuntun','Recent Posts Color'=>'Icolor Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ Tuntun','Recent Posts Decoration'=>'Ẹwà Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ Tuntun','Recent Posts HTML Tag'=>'Ẹya HTML Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ Tuntun','Recent Posts Icon Color'=>'Icolor Aami Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ Tuntun','Recent Posts Limit'=>'Iwọn Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ Tuntun','Recent Posts Line Height (px)'=>'Giga Ọkọ Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ Tuntun (px)','Recent Posts Order'=>'Iṣẹpọ Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ Tuntun','Recent Posts Size'=>'Iwọn Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ Tuntun','Recent Posts Style'=>'Iru Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ Tuntun','Recent Posts Transform'=>'Iyipada Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ Tuntun','Recent Posts Weight'=>'Iwọn Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ Tuntun','Recommendations for you'=>'Awọn Iyanjẹ fun ọ','Registered Author With User Account'=>'Onkọwe Ti a Forukọsilẹ Pẹlu Iṣẹ olumulo','Registered User'=>'Olumulo Ti a Forukọsilẹ','Registered User is required.'=>'Olumulo Ti a Forukọsilẹ nilo.','Remove %1$s Image'=>'Yọ %1$s Aworan','Remove %1s'=>'Yọ %1s','Remove Display Name Link'=>'Yọ Asopọ Orukọ Ifihan','Remove single author map restriction:'=>'Yọ idena maapu onkọwe kan:','Remove this image'=>'Yọ aworan yii','Reorder Fields'=>'Tun Ṣeto Awọn aaye','Reorder the fields by dragging them to the correct position and saving your changes.'=>'Tun ṣeto awọn aaye nipa gbigbe wọn si ipo to tọ ki o si fipamọ awọn ayipada rẹ.','Request status.'=>'Ipo ibeere.','Request Support'=>'Beere Atilẹyin','Required'=>'Nilo','Requirement'=>'Ibeere','Rest API'=>'REST API','Rest API support'=>'Atilẹyin REST API','Restore'=>'Da pada','Reviewer'=>'Atunwo','Reviewers'=>'Awọn ayẹwo','Reviews'=>'Awọn ayẹwo','Ridge'=>'Igi','Right'=>'Otun','Roles'=>'Iṣẹ','Roles available for Author Profiles:'=>'Awọn iṣẹ ti o wa fun Awọn profaili Akọwe:','Save Changes'=>'Fipamọ Awọn ayipada','Save for All Author Boxes'=>'Fipamọ fun Gbogbo Awọn Apoti Akọwe','Save for Current Author Box'=>'Fipamọ fun Apoti Akọwe Tẹlẹ','Schema Property'=>'I Properties Schema','Search'=>'Wa','Search %1s Icon'=>'Wa %1s Aami','Search %2$s'=>'Wa %2$s','Search Author Categories'=>'Wa Awọn ẹka Akọwe','Search Author Lists'=>'Wa Awọn atokọ Akọwe','Search Authors'=>'Wa Awọn Akọwe','Search Box'=>'Wa Apoti','Search for a fallback author'=>'Wa fun akọwe itẹsiwaju','Search for an author'=>'Wa fun akọwe','Search for an user'=>'Wa fun olumulo','Search results for &#8220;%s&#8221;'=>'%s: wa awọn ọrọ-ọrọ','Security error. Kindly reload this page and try again'=>'Aṣiṣe aabo. Jọwọ tun ṣe ikojọpọ oju-iwe yii ki o si gbiyanju lẹẹkansi','Security error. Kindly reload this page and try again.'=>'Aṣiṣe aabo. Jọwọ tun ṣe ikojọpọ oju-iwe yii ki o si gbiyanju lẹẹkansi.','Select %1s'=>'Yan %1s','Select a user'=>'Yan olumulo kan','Select an author box'=>'Yan apoti onkọwe kan','Select an option'=>'Yan aṣayan kan','Select an option to exclude selected user roles, author types, specific authors or author Categories from Author list.'=>'Yan aṣayan kan lati yọ awọn ipa olumulo ti a yan, awọn iru onkọwe, awọn onkọwe pato tabi Awọn ẹka onkọwe kuro ninu atokọ Onkọwe.','Select an option to limit the results to selected user roles, author types, specific authors or author Categories.'=>'Yan aṣayan kan lati dín awọn abajade si awọn ipa olumulo ti a yan, awọn iru onkọwe, awọn onkọwe pato tabi Awọn ẹka onkọwe.','Select Author Categories...'=>'Yan Awọn Ẹka Onkọwe...','Select Author Category'=>'Yan Ẹka Onkọwe','Select image'=>'Yan aworan','Select option'=>'Yan aṣayan','Select Post Type...'=>'Yan Iru Ifiweranṣẹ...','Select post types to include in recent posts. Leave empty to show all post types.'=>'Yan awọn iru ifiweranṣẹ lati fi kun ninu awọn ifiweranṣẹ tuntun. Fi silẹ laisi nkan lati fihan gbogbo awọn iru ifiweranṣẹ.','Select post types...'=>'Yan awọn iru ifiweranṣẹ...','Select Preview Post'=>'Yan Ifiweranṣẹ Igbasilẹ','Select roles'=>'Yan awọn ipa','Select some options'=>'Yan diẹ ninu awọn aṣayan','Select the default Category for this Author. This will be used when the Author is added to new posts.'=>'Yan Ẹka aiyipada fun Onkọwe yii. Eyi yoo ṣee lo nigbati a ba fi Onkọwe kun awọn ifiweranṣẹ tuntun.','Select Users'=>'Yan Awọn olumulo','Select which post types this category applies to. Leave empty for all post types.'=>'Yan iru awọn ifiweranṣẹ wo ni ẹka yii yẹ. Fi silẹ fun gbogbo iru awọn ifiweranṣẹ.','Selecting an option here will overwrite author boxes settings to match selected layout.'=>'Yiyan aṣayan kan nibi yoo kọ awọn eto apoti onkọwe silẹ lati ba apẹrẹ ti a yan mu.','Separate authors with commas'=>'Ya awọn onkọwe pẹlu awọn koma','Set %1$s Image'=>'Set %1$s Aworan','Settings'=>'Eto','Settings Imported Successfully!'=>'Eto ti gbe wọle ni aṣeyọri!','Settings updated successfully.'=>'Eto ti ṣe imudojuiwọn ni aṣeyọri.','Shortcode'=>'Koodu kukuru','Shortcode documentation.'=>'Iwe aṣẹ koodu kukuru.','Shortcodes'=>'Awọn koodu kukuru','Show "View all posts" link'=>'Fihan "Wo gbogbo awọn ifiweranṣẹ" ọna asopọ','Show a profile checkbox allowing Authors to be excluded from Author Boxes.'=>'Fihan apoti akọsilẹ kan ti ngbanilaaye awọn Onkọwe lati wa ni yọkuro lati awọn apoti onkọwe.','Show above the content:'=>'Fihan loke akoonu:','Show After'=>'Fihan Lẹhin','Show after an individual author'=>'Fihan lẹhin onkọwe kan','Show author bio:'=>'Fihan bio onkọwe:','Show Author Box selection:'=>'Fihan yiyan Apoti Onkọwe:','Show Author Categories'=>'Fihan Awọn Ẹka Onkọwe','Show author page title:'=>'Fihan akọle oju-iwe onkọwe:','Show Authors'=>'Fihan Awọn onkọwe','Show authors:'=>'Fihan awọn onkọwe:','Show Avatar'=>'Fihan Avatar','Show before an individual author'=>'Fihan ṣaaju onkọwe kọọkan','Show before author group'=>'Fihan ṣaaju ẹgbẹ onkọwe','Show below the content:'=>'Fihan ni isalẹ akoonu:','Show Biographical Info'=>'Fihan Alaye Igbesiaye','Show Box Title'=>'Fihan Akọle Apoti','Show category:'=>'Fihan ẹka:','Show comment counts:'=>'Fihan iye awọn asọye:','Show Display Name'=>'Fihan Orukọ Ifihan','Show email link:'=>'Fihan ọna ọna imeeli:','Show Even if No Recent Post'=>'Fihan Paapaa ti Ko si Ifiweranṣẹ Tuntun','Show excerpt:'=>'Fihan akopọ:','Show featured image:'=>'Fihan aworan ti a ṣe afihan:','Show in REST API'=>'Fihan ninu REST API','Show post date:'=>'Fihan ọjọ ifiweranṣẹ:','Show read more link:'=>'Fihan ọna ọna ka siwaju:','Show Recent Posts'=>'Fihan Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ Tuntun','Show Recent Posts Title'=>'Fihan Akọle Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ Tuntun','Show site link:'=>'Fihan ọna asopọ aaye:','Show tags:'=>'Fihan awọn afi:','Show username in the search field:'=>'Fihan orukọ olumulo ninu aaye ìwádìí:','Showcase your Authors with PublishPress Blocks'=>'Ṣe afihan Awọn onkọwe rẹ pẹlu PublishPress Blocks','Simple List'=>'Atokọ Rọrun','Simple list legacy layout Author Box:'=>'Atokọ Rọrun ti atunto atijọ Apo Onkọwe:','Simple Name Authors Block (Categories)'=>'Apo Orukọ Rọrun ti Awọn onkọwe (Ẹka)','Simple Name Authors Inline (Categories)'=>'Orukọ Rọrun ti Awọn onkọwe Inline (Ẹka)','Single'=>'Ẹyọkan','Single Title'=>'Àkọlé Ẹyọkan','Singular Name'=>'Orukọ Ẹyọkan','Singular name is required.'=>'Orukọ ẹyọkan jẹ dandan.','Size'=>'Iwọn','Slug'=>'Slug','Small-sized image (150px by 150px)'=>'Aworan ti iwọn kekere (150px nipasẹ 150px)','Social Profile?'=>'Profaili Awujọ?','Solid'=>'Iwọn','Sorry, the request returned an error.'=>'E ma binu, ìbéèrè náà dá aṣiṣe kan.','Sorry, this WordPress user is already mapped to another Author. By default, each user can only be connected to one Author profile.'=>'E ma binu, olumulo WordPress yii ti wa ni asopọ si onkọwe miiran tẹlẹ. Ni aiyipada, olumulo kọọkan le ni asopọ si profaili onkọwe kan ṣoṣo.','span'=>'span','Static Shortcode'=>'Koodu Iboju','Status'=>'Ipo','Sync author and user fields'=>'Sopọ awọn aaye onkọwe ati olumulo','Sync author and user URLs'=>'Sopọ awọn URL onkọwe ati olumulo','Synchronize PublishPress Authors Fields and user profile fields'=>'Sopọ Awọn aaye Onkọwe PublishPress ati awọn aaye profaili olumulo','Synchronize the author and user URLs'=>'Sopọ awọn URL onkọwe ati olumulo','Template generated successfuly!'=>'Àtẹ̀jáde àtẹ́yẹ̀wò ni aṣeyọrí!','Text'=>'Ọrọ','The authors data shortcode accepts field parameter such as: %1$s %2$s %3$s %4$s %5$s %6$s %7$s. You can see full details and parameters %8$s in this guide %9$s.'=>'Koodu data awọn onkọwe gba paramita aaye bi: %1$s %2$s %3$s %4$s %5$s %6$s %7$s. O le rii awọn alaye kikun ati awọn paramita %8$s ninu itọsọna yii %9$s.','The original size of the uploaded image'=>'Iwọn atilẹba ti aworan ti a gbe silẹ','The SEO Framework Integration'=>'Iṣọpọ SEO Framework','The slug is used in code to reference this author field. It is all lowercase and contains only letters, numbers, and hyphens.'=>'Slag ni a lo ninu koodu lati tọka si aaye onkọwe yii. O jẹ gbogbo lẹta kekere ati pe o ni awọn lẹta, awọn nọmba, ati awọn hyphens nikan.','Theme'=>'Akori','There are no PublishPress modules registered'=>'Ko si awọn modulu PublishPress ti a forukọsilẹ','There is one final option to mention. This is mostly useful if you\'re using a theme or page builder to customize the Author profile pages you find at URLs such as /author/username/. You can use the following shortcode on the authors page to display the profile of the current author. You just need to add the parameter %s.'=>'Iṣeeṣe ikẹhin kan wa lati mẹnuba. Eyi jẹ lilo julọ ti o ba nlo akori tabi oludasilẹ oju-iwe lati ṣe akanṣe awọn oju-iwe profaili Onkọwe ti o rii ni awọn URL bii /author/username/. O le lo koodu atẹle lori oju-iwe awọn onkọwe lati ṣafihan profaili onkọwe lọwọlọwọ. O kan nilo lati fi paramita %s kun.','This action can reset the PublishPress Authors data before using other maintenance options. Guest authors are author profiles that are not mapped to a WordPress user account. This action will delete all guest authors.'=>'Igbese yii le tunṣe data awọn onkọwe PublishPress ṣaaju ki o to lo awọn aṣayan itọju miiran. Awọn onkọwe alejo ni awọn profaili onkọwe ti ko ni itumọ si akọọlẹ olumulo WordPress. Igbese yii yoo pa gbogbo awọn onkọwe alejo.','This action can reset the PublishPress Authors data before using other maintenance options. It will delete all author profiles that are mapped to a WordPress user account. This will not delete the WordPress user accounts, but any links between the posts and author profiles will be lost.'=>'Igbese yii le tunṣe data awọn onkọwe PublishPress ṣaaju ki o to lo awọn aṣayan itọju miiran. Yoo pa gbogbo awọn profaili onkọwe ti a ti ni itumọ si akọọlẹ olumulo WordPress. Eyi ko ni pa awọn akọọlẹ olumulo WordPress, ṣugbọn eyikeyi awọn ọna asopọ laarin awọn ifiweranṣẹ ati awọn profaili onkọwe yoo sọnu.','This action will copy the authors from the plugin Co-Authors Plus allowing you to migrate to PublishPress Authors without losing any data. This action can be run multiple times.'=>'Igbese yii yoo daakọ awọn onkọwe lati afikun Co-Authors Plus ti o fun ọ laaye lati ṣe gbigbe si awọn Onkọwe PublishPress laisi padanu eyikeyi data. Igbese yii le ṣee ṣe ni ọpọlọpọ igba.','This action will copy the authors from the plugin Molongui Authorship allowing you to migrate to PublishPress Authors without losing any data including post author relation. This action can be run multiple times.'=>'Igbese yii yoo daakọ awọn onkọwe lati afikun Molongui Authorship ti o fun ọ laaye lati ṣe gbigbe si awọn Onkọwe PublishPress laisi padanu eyikeyi data pẹlu ibasepọ onkọwe ifiweranṣẹ. Igbese yii le ṣee ṣe ni ọpọlọpọ igba.','This avatar will be used as default avatar instead of gravatar where no custom avatar is added to profile.'=>'Aworan yii yoo lo gẹgẹbi aworan aiyipada dipo gravatar nibiti ko si aworan aṣa ti a fi kun si profaili.','This description appears under the fields and helps users understand their choice.'=>'Apejuwe yi han ni isalẹ awọn aaye ati iranlọwọ awọn olumulo lati loye yiyan wọn.','This feature will add the SameAs property to this link so that search engines realize that the social profile is connected to this author.'=>'Iṣẹ-ṣiṣe yii yoo fi ohun-ini SameAs kun ọna ọna yii ki awọn ẹrọ wiwa le mọ pe profaili awujọ ni asopọ si onkọwe yii.','This feature will add the target=”_blank” attribute to your link.'=>'Iṣẹ-ṣiṣe yii yoo fi ohun-ini target=”_blank” kun ọna ọna rẹ.','This forms part of the URL for the author’s profile page. If you choose a Mapped User, this URL is taken from the user’s account and can not be changed.'=>'Eyi jẹ apakan ti URL fun oju-iwe profaili onkọwe. Ti o ba yan Olumulo Mapped, URL yii ni a mu lati akọọlẹ olumulo ati pe ko le yipada.','This is a quick preview of this Author List. Test on frontend pages to see exactly how it looks with your theme.'=>'Eyi jẹ iṣafihan iyara ti Atokọ Onkọwe yii. Ṣe idanwo lori awọn oju-iwe iwaju lati rii daju bi o ṣe n wo pẹlu akori rẹ.','This is useful if you use legacy shortcode %s'=>'Eyi wulo ti o ba lo koodu kukuru atijọ %s','This is useful when linking to an email, URL, or phone number. For example, \'mailto:\', \'https://\' or \'tel:\' can be added as the prefix.'=>'Eyi wulo nigbati o ba so pọ si imeeli, URL, tabi nọmba foonu. Fun apẹẹrẹ, \'mailto:\', \'https://\' tabi \'tel:\' le ṣee fi kun gẹgẹ bi akọle.','This name is used in several default displays and some search engine integrations.'=>'Orukọ yii ni a lo ni ọpọlọpọ awọn ifihan aiyipada ati diẹ ninu awọn iṣọpọ ẹrọ wiwa.','This option is showing because you do not have a WordPress user selected as an author. For some tasks, it can be helpful to have a user selected here. This user will not be visible on the front of your site.'=>'Yiyan yii n ṣafihan nitori ko ni Olumulo WordPress ti a yan gẹgẹ bi onkọwe. Fun diẹ ninu awọn iṣẹ, o le wulo lati ni olumulo ti a yan nibi. Olumulo yii ko ni han ni iwaju aaye rẹ.','This plugin can be deleted.'=>'A le pa ẹrọ afikun yii run.','This setting may be disabled for users who can not edit others posts.'=>'Iṣeto yii le jẹ ti a ko ṣiṣẹ fun awọn olumulo ti ko le ṣatunkọ awọn ifiweranṣẹ miiran.','This will allows you map a WordPress user to more than one author. Don\'t use this feature unless requested to do so by the PublishPress team. This plugin works better when authors and users are paired one-to-one.'=>'Eyi yoo jẹ ki o ṣe afiwe Olumulo WordPress si ju onkọwe kan lọ. Ma ṣe lo iṣẹ-ṣiṣe yii ayafi ti a beere lati ṣe bẹ nipasẹ ẹgbẹ PublishPress. Ẹrọ afikun yii n ṣiṣẹ dara julọ nigbati awọn onkọwe ati awọn olumulo ba ni apapọ ọkan-si-ọkan.','This will create author categories table if missing and add default categories.'=>'Eyi yoo ṣẹda tabili awọn ẹka onkọwe ti o ba padanu ati fi awọn ẹka aiyipada kun.','This will display author in an inline format side by side instead of block format.'=>'Eyi yoo ṣe afihan onkọwe ni ọna inline lẹgbẹẹ dipo ọna bulọọki.','This will display author page title.'=>'Eyi yoo ṣe afihan akọle oju-iwe onkọwe.','This will display the author bio.'=>'Eyi yoo ṣe afihan bio onkọwe.','This will display the authors box at the end of the content.'=>'Eyi yoo ṣe afihan apoti awọn onkọwe ni ipari akoonu.','This will display the authors box at the top of the content.'=>'Eyi yoo ṣe afihan apoti awọn onkọwe ni oke akoonu.','This will display the authors email in the author box.'=>'Eyi yoo ṣe afihan imeeli awọn onkọwe ni apoti onkọwe.','This will display the authors site in the author box.'=>'Eyi yoo ṣe afihan aaye ayelujara awọn onkọwe ni apoti onkọwe.','This will display the authors.'=>'Yi yoo ṣe afihan awọn onkọwe.','This will display the categories.'=>'Yi yoo ṣe afihan awọn ẹka.','This will display the comment count.'=>'Yi yoo ṣe afihan iye awọn asọye.','This will display the excerpt.'=>'Yi yoo ṣe afihan akopọ naa.','This will display the featured image.'=>'Yi yoo ṣe afihan aworan ti a ṣe afihan.','This will display the published date.'=>'Yi yoo ṣe afihan ọjọ ti a tẹjade.','This will display the read more link.'=>'Yi yoo ṣe afihan ọna asopọ ka siwaju.','This will display the tags.'=>'Yi yoo ṣe afihan awọn aami.','This will find all the users in a role and create author profiles for them. You can choose the roles using the "Automatically create author profiles" setting.'=>'Yi yoo wa gbogbo awọn olumulo ninu ipa kan ki o ṣẹda awọn profaili onkọwe fun wọn. O le yan awọn ipa nipa lilo eto "Ṣẹda awọn profaili onkọwe laifọwọyi".','This will load Font Awesome icons for use in Author Boxes.'=>'Yi yoo gba awọn aami Font Awesome lati lo ninu Awọn Apoti Onkọwe.','This will make the featured image clickable and link to the post.'=>'Eyi yoo jẹ ki aworan ti a ṣe afihan le tẹ ati so pọ si ifiweranṣẹ.','This will remove the Authors Box in "Quick Edit".'=>'Yi yoo yọ Apoti Onkọwe ni "Ṣatunkọ Pẹlẹpẹlẹ".','This will update all the author profiles in PublishPress Authors to match the default WordPress fields for each user.'=>'Yi yoo mu gbogbo awọn profaili onkọwe ni PublishPress Authors pọ si lati ba awọn aaye WordPress aiyipada mu fun ọkọọkan olumulo.','This will update all the Author URLs in PublishPress Authors to match the default WordPress URLs for each user.'=>'Yi yoo mu gbogbo awọn URL Onkọwe ni PublishPress Authors pọ si lati ba awọn URL WordPress aiyipada mu fun ọkọọkan olumulo.','This WordPress user is already mapped to another author.'=>'Olumulo WordPress yi ti wa ni ipamọ tẹlẹ si onkọwe miiran.','TikTok'=>'TikTok','Title'=>'Akole','Title for the author box:'=>'Akole fun apoti onkọwe:','To display a search box for authors, use %1$s .'=>'Lati ṣe afihan apoti wiwa fun awọn onkọwe, lo %1$s .','To further customize the order of results, use %1$s or %2$s .'=>'Lati tun ṣe akanṣe aṣẹ awọn esi, lo %1$s tabi %2$s .','To order the results based on post count, use %1$s . To order the results by name, use %2$s . Alternatively, you can order by profile fields like %3$s, %4$s etc'=>'Lati paṣẹ awọn esi da lori iye ifiweranṣẹ, lo %1$s . Lati paṣẹ awọn esi nipasẹ orukọ, lo %2$s . Ni ilodi si, o le paṣẹ nipasẹ awọn aaye profaili bii %3$s, %4$s ati bẹbẹ lọ','Trash'=>'Ibi idọti','Trash %s'=>'Ibi idọti %s','Two Columns (Categories)'=>'Ìtòsọ́nà Méjì (Ìṣàkóso)','Type'=>'Iru','Ultimate Member Integration'=>'Isopọ Ẹgbẹ Olumulo','Ultimate_Post Integration'=>'Isopọ Ultimate_Post','Underline'=>'Iṣẹlẹ','Update'=>'Imudojuiwọn','Update Author'=>'Imudojuiwọn Onkọwe','Update post count'=>'Imudojuiwọn iye ifiweranṣẹ','Updated %d authors'=>'Imudojuiwọn %d awọn onkọwe','Updated %d of %d authors...'=>'Imudojuiwọn %d ti %d awọn onkọwe...','Updated %d of %d posts...'=>'Imudojuiwọn %d ti %d awọn ifiweranṣẹ...','Updating author field on posts...'=>'Nṣiṣẹ imudojuiwọn aaye onkọwe lori awọn ifiweranṣẹ...','Updating authors slug...'=>'Nṣiṣẹ imudojuiwọn slug awọn onkọwe...','Upgrade to Pro'=>'Gbigba si Pro','Uppercase'=>'Iwe nla','Use as %1$s Image'=>'Lo gẹgẹbi %1$s Aworan','Use the Content Display block to show your posts in many beautiful layouts.'=>'Lo bulọọki Ifihan Akọ content lati fi awọn ifiweranṣẹ rẹ han ni ọpọlọpọ awọn apẹrẹ ẹlẹwa.','User Account'=>'Akọọlẹ Olumulo','Users'=>'Awọn olumulo','Users Authors'=>'Awọn olumulo Onkọwe','View'=>'Wo','View %1$s'=>'Wo %1$s','View All Posts'=>'Wo Gbogbo Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ','View all posts'=>'Wo gbogbo awọn ifiweranṣẹ','View All Posts Label'=>'Wo Gbogbo Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ Àkọlé','View All Posts Link Alignment'=>'Wo Gbogbo Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ Ẹgbẹ Asopọ','View All Posts Link Background Color'=>'Wo Gbogbo Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ Ẹgbẹ Asopọ Awọ Abẹlẹ','View All Posts Link Decoration'=>'Wo Gbogbo Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ Ẹgbẹ Asopọ Iṣe','View All Posts Link Hover Color'=>'Wo Gbogbo Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ Ẹgbẹ Asopọ Awọ Igbẹkẹle','View All Posts Link HTML Tag'=>'Wo Gbogbo Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ Ẹgbẹ Asopọ HTML Tag','View All Posts Link Line Height (px)'=>'Wo Gbogbo Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ Ẹgbẹ Asopọ Giga Ọna (px)','View All Posts Link Meta Color'=>'Wo Gbogbo Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ Ẹgbẹ Asopọ Awọ Meta','View All Posts Link Size'=>'Wo Gbogbo Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ Ẹgbẹ Asopọ Iwọn','View All Posts Link Style'=>'Wo Gbogbo Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ Ẹgbẹ Asopọ Ara','View All Posts Link Transform'=>'Wo Gbogbo Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ Ẹgbẹ Asopọ Iyipada','View All Posts Link Weight'=>'Wo Gbogbo Awọn Ifiweranṣẹ Ẹgbẹ Asopọ Iwuwo','View all posts Row'=>'Wo gbogbo awọn ifiweranṣẹ Ipele','View Author'=>'Wo Onkọwe','View Knowledge Base'=>'Wo Ibi Imọ','View sample Author Page'=>'Wo àpẹẹrẹ Ojúewé Onkọwe','Website'=>'Ojú-ìwé','With PublishPress Authors Pro, you can add new fields for social networks and more.'=>'Pẹlu PublishPress Authors Pro, o le fi awọn aaye tuntun kun fun awọn nẹtiwọọki awujọ ati bẹbẹ lọ.','With this shortcode you can display the author box in any part of the content. '=>'Pẹlu shortcode yii o le fihan apoti onkọwe ni eyikeyi apakan ti akoonu.','With this shortcode you can display the author names or any profile field in any part of the content.'=>'Pẹlu shortcode yii o le fihan awọn orukọ onkọwe tabi eyikeyi aaye profaili ni eyikeyi apakan ti akoonu.','With this shortcode, you can show all the authors together in a single display.'=>'Pẹlu shortcode yii, o le fihan gbogbo awọn onkọwe papọ ni ifihan kan ṣoṣo.','WPEngine Integration'=>'Isopọ WPEngine','WYSIWYG Editor'=>'Ẹlẹda WYSIWYG','X'=>'X','Yes'=>'Bẹẹni','Yes, this is a Social Profile'=>'Bẹẹni, eyi jẹ Profaili Awujọ','Yoast SEO Integration'=>'Isopọ Yoast SEO','You are not allowed to create Author Boxes.'=>'A ko gba ọ laaye lati ṣẹda Awọn Aago onkọwe.','You are not allowed to duplicate this Author Box.'=>'A ko gba ọ laaye lati daakọ Aago onkọwe yii.','You can also decide to return an array list of authors by using user_objects="true" which will return all the authors object data as an array. You can check full details and sample usage %2$s in this guide%3$s.'=>'O tun le pinnu lati da akojọ ti awọn onkọwe pada nipa lilo user_objects="true" eyiti yoo da gbogbo awọn nkan onkọwe pada gẹgẹbi akojọ. O le ṣayẹwo alaye kikun ati lilo àpẹẹrẹ %2$s ni itọsọna yii%3$s.','You can also decide whether or not to show the main title, using %1$s or %2$s .'=>'O tun le pinnu boya lati fihan akọle akọkọ, nipa lilo %1$s tabi %2$s .','You can also show a dropdown menu that allows users to search on specific author fields. You can add fields to the dropdown using %1$s . This requires the search box to be active.'=>'O tun le fihan akojọ aṣayan aṣayan ti o fun awọn olumulo laaye lati wa lori awọn aaye onkọwe pato. O le fi awọn aaye kun akojọ aṣayan nipa lilo %1$s . Eyi nilo ki apoti wiwa wa ni iṣe.','You can also specify the separator to be used for mulitple authors data.'=>'O tun le ṣalaye akọtọ ti a yoo lo fun data awọn onkọwe pupọ.','You can choose the number of authors per page using %1$s . %2$s Pagination will be automatically added if required.'=>'O le yan nọmba awọn onkọwe fun oju-iwe nipa lilo %1$s . %2$s Ipinpin yoo ti wa ni afikun laifọwọyi ti o ba nilo.','You can create Author Boxes where Authors are grouped into their categories.'=>'O le ṣẹda Awọn Apoti Onkọwe nibiti awọn Onkọwe ti wa ni ẹgbẹ sinu awọn ẹka wọn.','You can define the number of layout columns by using %1$s to show authors in 2 column.'=>'O le ṣalaye nọmba awọn ọwọn apẹrẹ nipa lilo %1$s lati fihan awọn onkọwe ni ọwọn 2.','You can limit the author list to users with a published post within a specific period using %1$s . This accept english date value like 1 week ago, 1 month ago, 6 months ago, 1 year ago etc.'=>'O le dènà atokọ onkọwe si awọn olumulo ti o ni ifiweranṣẹ ti a tẹjade laarin akoko kan pato nipa lilo %1$s . Eyi gba iye ọjọ English bi 1 ọsẹ sẹyin, 1 oṣù sẹyin, 6 oṣù sẹyin, 1 ọdún sẹyin ati bẹbẹ lọ.','You can limit the result to only authors who are assigned to posts by using %1$s . %2$s Alternatively, use %3$s to show all authors, including those without any posts.'=>'O le dènà abajade si awọn onkọwe nikan ti a yàn si awọn ifiweranṣẹ nipa lilo %1$s . %2$s Ni omiiran, lo %3$s lati fi gbogbo awọn onkọwe han, pẹlu awọn ti ko ni awọn ifiweranṣẹ.','You can limit the result to only guest authors by using %1$s . %2$s Alternatively, %3$s will show only authors with a WordPress account.'=>'O le dènà abajade si awọn onkọwe alejo nikan nipa lilo %1$s . %2$s Ni omiiran, %3$s yoo fi awọn onkọwe nikan ti o ni akọọlẹ WordPress han.','You can load the authors belonging to a specific author categories by providing the category slug or slugs separated by comma for more than one category.'=>'O le gbe awọn onkọwe ti o ni ibatan si awọn ẹka onkọwe pato nipa fifunni ni slug ẹka tabi awọn slugs ti a ya sọtọ nipasẹ koma fun diẹ ẹ sii ju ẹka kan lọ.','You can load the authors for a specific author by providing the author term id for both guest and user author. For example, this shortcode will load the author with term id of 32'=>'O le gbe awọn onkọwe fun onkọwe pato nipa fifunni ni id ọrọ onkọwe fun mejeeji onkọwe alejo ati onkọwe olumulo. Fun apẹẹrẹ, shortcode yii yoo gbe onkọwe pẹlu id ọrọ ti 32','You can load the authors for a specific post, even if you are not in that post currently. For example, this shortcode will load the authors for the post with the ID of 32.'=>'O le gbe awọn onkọwe fun ifiweranṣẹ pato, paapaa ti o ko ba wa ninu ifiweranṣẹ yẹn lọwọlọwọ. Fun apẹẹrẹ, shortcode yii yoo gbe awọn onkọwe fun ifiweranṣẹ pẹlu ID ti 32.','You can load the authors for a specific user by providing the user id. For example, this shortcode will load the author with user id of 32'=>'O le gbe awọn onkọwe fun olumulo pato nipa fifunni ni id olumulo. Fun apẹẹrẹ, shortcode yii yoo gbe onkọwe pẹlu id olumulo ti 32','You can retrieve a specific author by providing the author\'s term ID. For example, this shortcode will load the author with the term ID of 102.'=>'O le gba onkọwe pato nipa fifunni ni ID ọrọ onkọwe. Fun apẹẹrẹ, shortcode yii yoo gbe onkọwe pẹlu ID ọrọ ti 102.','You can retrieve authors belonging to a specific Author Category by providing the category slug or slugs. Separate multiple slugs with a comma.'=>'O le gba awọn onkọwe ti o ni ibatan si Ẹka Onkọwe pato nipa fifunni ni slug ẹka tabi awọn slugs. Ya sọtọ ọpọlọpọ awọn slugs pẹlu koma.','You can specify a separator such as \',\' to separate authors. This field accepts basic HTML.'=>'O le ṣe afihan eya kan gẹgẹ bi \',\' lati ya awọn onkọwe. Ọrọ yii gba HTML ipilẹ.','You can specify layout by using author boxes layout slug. You can see full details of each layout option %1$s in this guide %2$s.'=>'O le ṣe afihan apẹrẹ nipa lilo slug eya apoti onkọwe. O le wo awọn alaye kikun ti gbogbo aṣayan apẹrẹ %1$s ninu itọsọna yii %2$s.','You can specify layout by using author boxes layout slug. You can see full details of each layout option %1$s in this guide %2$s. %3$s %4$s This shortcode also provides two custom layouts: %5$s %6$s.'=>'O le ṣe afihan apẹrẹ nipa lilo slug eya apoti onkọwe. O le wo awọn alaye kikun ti gbogbo aṣayan apẹrẹ %1$s ninu itọsọna yii %2$s. %3$s %4$s Shortcode yii tun n pese awọn apẹrẹ aṣa meji: %5$s %6$s.','You can use basic HTML in this field. For example: Read Time %1s.'=>'O le lo HTML ipilẹ ni aaye yii. Fun apẹẹrẹ: Akoko kika %1s.','You can use multiple class names. Leave a space between each class.'=>'O le lo orukọ kilasi pupọ. Fi aaye silẹ laarin kilasi kọọkan.','You can use this data to export your author box design and import it to a new site.'=>'O le lo data yii lati gbe apẹrẹ apoti onkọwe rẹ jade ki o si gbe e si aaye tuntun.','You cannot edit an author profile linked to an administrator account.'=>'O ko le ṣatunkọ profaili onkọwe ti o ni asopọ si iroyin alakoso.','You cannot edit author mapped to administrator account.'=>'O ko le ṣatunkọ onkọwe ti a ṣe pọ si iroyin alakoso.','You do not have necessary permissions to complete this action.'=>'O ko ni awọn aṣẹ to ṣe pataki lati pari iṣẹ yii.','You do not have permission to edit this author profile because it is linked to a user account you do not have permission to edit.'=>'O ko ni aṣẹ lati ṣatunkọ profaili onkọwe yii nitori pe o ni asopọ si iroyin olumulo ti o ko ni aṣẹ lati ṣatunkọ.','You do not have permission to edit this author.'=>'O ko ni aṣẹ lati ṣatunkọ onkọwe yii.','You do not have permission to perform this action'=>'O ko ni aṣẹ lati ṣe iṣe yii','You need to enable atleast one author category to use this feature.'=>'O nilo lati mu ki o kere ju ẹka onkọwe kan ṣiṣẹ lati lo ẹya yii.','You\'re using PublishPress Authors Free. The Pro version has more features and support. %sUpgrade to Pro%s'=>'Iwọ nlo PublishPress Authors Free. Ẹya Pro ni awọn ẹya diẹ sii ati atilẹyin. %sṢe igbesoke si Pro%s','YouTube'=>'YouTube','Author Box post type name%2$s'=>'%2$s','custom field post type menu name%2$s'=>'%2$s','Custom Field post type name%2$s'=>'%2$s','custom layout post type menu name%2$s'=>'%2$s','singular author box post type name%1$s'=>'%1$s','singular custom field post type name%1$s'=>'%1$s','taxonomy general nameAuthors'=>'Awọn onkọwe','taxonomy singular nameAuthor'=>'Onkọwe']];